Richard Burgon, MP for East Leeds was speaking at last night's pre-Autumn Statement People's Assembly Against Austerity demonstration in London; 

"I believe we that we are on the cusp of the potential of real change. I think that people have had enough."

Don't forget to tweet your #DearGeorge message to @George_Osborne today, using the hashtag #NoWorkPenalty
